# ==========================================
# Xilinx Vivado General Ignore List
# ==========================================

# Vivado generated directories (Logs, reports, caches, etc.)
*.cache/
*.hw/
*.ip_user_files/
*.runs/
*.sim/
*.xpe/
.Xil/

# Vivado generated log and journal files
*.jou
*.log
*.str
*.pb
*.wdb
*.vcd
*.a

# Bitstreams and Binaries (Ignore general ones, unless specifically versioned)
*.bit
*.bin
*.svf

# Checkpoint files
*.dcp

*~
*.bak

# ==========================================
# Project Specific (Keep track of BD & IP repo)
# ==========================================
# Ignore the auto-generated HDL wrapper if you prefer regenerating it, 
# but usually it's fine to track it. 
# We explicitly ignore the 'bd' auto-generated temporary folders if any, 
# but KEEP the .bd file itself.

# Ignore Vitis / Software workspace temp files (if you use it later)
.metadata/
RemoteSystemsTempFiles/
*.elf

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

.vscode/
__pycache__/
*.pyc